HEADWORD: Interpunction
<hw>In`ter*punc"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>interpunctio</ets>, fr. <ets>interpungere</ets>,
<ets>interppunctum</ets>, to interpoint. See <er>Inter-</er>, and
<er>Point</er>.]</ety> <def>The insertion of points between words or
sentences; punctuation.</def>⟦br⟧
